# Traffic Light Controller using FSM

## Overview

This project implements a Traffic Light Controller using a Finite State Machine (FSM) in Verilog HDL.

## States

* RED (100)
* GREEN (010)
* YELLOW (001)

## State Transition

RED → GREEN → YELLOW → RED

## Tools Used

* Verilog HDL
* Icarus Verilog
* GTKWave

## Verification

The design was verified using a Verilog testbench and waveform analysis.

